        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For API infrastructure teams, evaluating model performance is critical for efficient deployment. The LTX-2.3 22B Distilled INT8 benchmark offers insights into a quantized, distilled variant of the 22B parameter model, designed to reduce latency and memory overhead while maintaining accuracy. This post covers practical guidance on leveraging this model in production, from benchmark analysis to integration tactics."
          }
